Package: cdmAcm0009
Title: Implementation of CDM Large-Scale Methodology ACM0009
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Christiaan", family = "Pauw", email = "christiaan.pauw@gmal.com", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Provides helper tools for applying the Clean Development Mechanism methodology ACM0009 "Fuel switch from coal and/or petroleum fuels to natural gas". The package exposes applicability checks, fuel switching emission equations, monitoring data aggregation utilities, simulation helpers, and meta-estimators to support reproducible greenhouse gas accounting for thermal power plant conversions to natural gas.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
